506
00:29:45.440 --> 00:29:48.280
Listen. I don't know if you're
having some sort of breakdown.

507
00:29:48.360 --> 00:29:50.080
I'm not having a fucking breakdown.

508
00:29:50.160 --> 00:29:52.200
Jesus. I take a few days away
